Package: libgusb
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: libc (>= 1.1.8), ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: GObject wrappers for libusb-1.0
 libgusb provides GObject wrappers for libusb-1.0 that make it easy to 
 do asynchronous control, bulk and interrupt transfers with proper 
 cancellation and integration into a mainloop.
 .
 This package provides the libgusb shared library.

Package: libgusb-dev
Section: libdevel
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: libgusb (= ${binary:Version}), libusb-dev, glib2-dev
Description: Development headers and static libraries for libgusb
 This package provides libgusb.a, pkgconfig data and header files required 
 for development using libgusb.
